# Courier Aggregator Web Platform 🚚

A full-stack logistics management website built for a real courier aggregator 
business in Pune. Inspired by industry platforms like OCCPL, DHL, and DTDC.

## 🎯 Features

- 📦 Shipment booking & management
- 🗄️ Database-driven order tracking
- 👤 Customer & admin portal
- 🔍 Real-time shipment status lookup
- 📍 Multi-courier aggregation support

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Frontend:** PHP, HTML, CSS
- **Backend:** PHP
- **Database:** MySQL

## 💼 Context

Built as a freelance project for a family-owned courier aggregator business.
Designed to match the functionality of enterprise logistics platforms.

